--------------------------------------------------------
README: 201101186, 201101101
--------------------------------------------------------

Part1:
To classify images under croppedYale Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part1

Part1_verif:
To verify a given image from croppedYale Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part1_verif Data/yaleB04/yaleB04_P00A+020E-10.pgm 1

Part2:
To classify images under CMU-PIE Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part2

Part2_verif:
To verify a given image under CMU-PIE Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part2_verif 622.png 32

Part3_yale:
To use SVM instead of K-NN for classification, based on croppedYale Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part3_yale

Part3_cmu:
To use SVM instead of K-NN for classification, based on CMU-PIE Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part3_cmu

Part4:
To reconstruct an image of a given image, based on the croppedYale Dataset.
Running
~~~~~~~
>> part4
